# Scenario 04 — full-system stress.
#
# YOLOv5n + face_recognition + synthetic person-event load. Driven by
# synthetic_load.sh which loops a pre-recorded person walk-by clip into
# a parallel RTSP path; the worker reads from that path instead of /cam.
#
# Pre-flight (operator, one-time):
#   1. Engine pre-build: same as 02-yolo-416.
#   2. Test footage: place a 10-30 s walk-by MP4 at
#      /home/israel/HomeCameraSystem/soak/test_footage.mp4
#      Easiest source: download an existing event clip from the PWA
#      (or curl /api/events/<id>/clip).
#   3. encodings.pkl present — face_recognition runs only when known
#      faces are loaded. CAPTURE-only mode (cv2 fallback) is also
#      acceptable for the soak; either way the recognize_in_crop hot
#      path runs.
#
# DETECT_SOURCE points the worker at the synthetic stream. Falls back
# to /cam after run_scenario.sh removes this override at end.
DETECT_MODEL=yolov5n
DETECT_ACTIVE_FPS=3.0
DETECT_IDLE_FPS=1.0
DETECT_SOURCE=rtsp://localhost:8554/stress
